sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as NguoiDung
participant Client as UngDungWeb
participant AiSvc as AiTaskService
participant Queue as RabbitMQ
participant Worker as AiTaskWorker
participant LLM as Ollama
participant AiDb as Mongo_AiTaskExtraction

Note over User,AiDb: Chặng 1 - Trích xuất đề xuất task
User->>Client: Chọn message cần trích xuất
Client->>AiSvc: POST /api/ai-tasks/extract
AiSvc->>AiDb: Lưu extraction queued
AiSvc->>Queue: Publish task-ai.extract
AiSvc-->>Client: 202 accepted
Queue->>Worker: Consume job
Worker->>LLM: Suy luận task draft
Worker->>AiDb: Lưu draft + confidence
